{"tid":613783,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"中資股支持者保皇狗打手關愛座hunter放生保皇狗","createTime":"2018-04-02T03:52:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T04:25:27.000Z","uid":38523,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"53c9922e154c9783cc4f9a5cf366729d4a15231c","tid":613783,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T03:52:18.000Z","msg":"入來呢度睇睇咪知囉<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/613281/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/613281/page/1</a><br />\n57vs12 大部分人都認同買中祺股令中國得益<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/613331/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/613331/page/1</a><br />\n學人拋書包<br />\n最後都係比人駁到收檔<br />\n之後<br />\n建制派議員發聲明譴責戴耀廷要求向公眾認錯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/613592/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/613592/page/1</a><br />\n中資股支持者保皇狗打手關愛座hunter唔去屌<br />\n反而去屌泛民唔出聲<br />\n<br />\n又自創白票本土<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/610626/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/610626/page/1</a><br />\n比我踢爆佢開分身／放生保皇狗後<br />\n比人陸續踢爆唔合佢意就係五毛 泛民打手<br />\n依加終於到我都比佢話係五毛<br />\n但由於冇位入我<br />\n睇見我反白票<br />\n就自創左個&ldquo;白票本土&rdquo;<br />\n所以我就順理成章地因為反白票變成反本土<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n買中資+玩分身+放生保皇狗+屈本土做白票<br />\n你反白票就變反本土<br />\n佢係咩人大家心知<br />\n我預左佢又入來又用泛民轉移視線"},{"pid":"a770cda7b90cbf1abe70cd3f5f4f636e5a23decf","tid":613783,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T03:56:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">樓主泛民打手開十個post狙擊我<br />\n都唔敢面對泛民賣港<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"96dc9ff1f4e30061cc875657a0ed8488da597565","tid":613783,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T03:56:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌我炒股<br />\n都唔敢屌泛民賣港<im